StepDetails.name: Counseling and Seat Allocation
StepDetails.description:
Register for JoSAA Counseling: Once you qualify for JEE Advanced, register for the Joint Seat Allocation Authority (JoSAA) counseling. It handles seat allocation for IITs and other top engineering institutions.

Choice Filling: During counseling, select IIT Madras as one of your choices based on your rank and preferences.

Seat Allocation: Based on your rank, availability of seats, and choices, you'll be allocated a seat in IITs, including IIT Madras.
